\c 42
\s Jobho anozvininipisa
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapindura Jehovha ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Ndinoziva kuti munogona zvese\x + Mat. 19.26.\x*, uye hakuna zano\x + 21.27. 17.11. Zvir. 1.4.\x* ringadziviswa kwamuri\x + Gen.. 11.6.\x*.
\v 3 Ndiani uyu anodzikatira zano asina zivo\x + 38.2.\x*? Naizvozvo ndakataura zvandaiva ndisinganzwisisi, zvinhu zvinoshamisa zvikuru kwandiri, zvandaiva ndisingazivi\x + Map. 131.1. Map. 40.5. 139.6.\x*.
\v 4 Inzwai henyu, zvino ndichataura ini. Ndichakubvunzai, uye muchandizivisa\x + 38.3. 40.7.\x*.
\v 5 Ndakakunzwai nekunzwa kwenzeve, asi ikozvino ziso rangu rinokuonai\x + Map. 18.45.\x*.
\v 6 Naizvozvo\x + 40.4.\x* ndino\add zvi\add*sema\x + 36.5.\x*, uye ndinozvidemba muguruva\x + 30.19. Gen.. 18.27.\x* nemumadota\x + 30.19. Gen.. 18.27.\x*\x + 2.8.\x*.
\s Jobho anodzoserwa mufaro wake wese
\p
\v 7 Zvino kwakati shure kwekutaura kwaJehovha mashoko awa kuna Jobho, kuti Jehovha wakati kuna Erifazi muTemani\x + 2.11.\x*: Kutsamwa kwangu kunopfutira iwe neshamwari dzako mbiri, nokuti hamuna kutaura pamusoro pangu zvakarurama semuranda wangu Jobho\x + 42.8. Map. 5.9.\x*.
\v 8 Naizvozvo ikozvino zvitorerei nzombe diki nomwe nemakondohwe manomwe, mugoenda kumuranda wangu Jobho\x + Num.. 23.1. 1 Makor. 15.26.\x*, mugozvipira chipo chinopiswa\x + 1.5.\x*. Zvino muranda wangu Jobho achakunyengetererai; nokuti zvirokwazvo ndichagamuchira chiso chake\x + Gen.. 20.17. Jak. 5.16.\x*, zvimwe ndikubatei \add se\add*upenzi \add hwenyu\add*; nokuti hamuna kutaura pamusoro pangu zvakarurama semuranda wangu Jobho\x + 42.8. Map. 5.9.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino Erifazi muTemani naBhiridhadhi muShuhi \add na\add*Zofari muNaama vakaenda vakaita sekureva kwaJehovha kwavari. Jehovha ndokugamuchira chiso chaJobho\x + 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Jehovha wakashandura utapwa hwaJobho paaiva anyengeterera shamwari dzake\x + Map. 14.7. 53.6. 85.1. 126.1. Jer. 30.3,18. 31.23. 32.44. 33.7,11,26. Eze. 39.25. Hos. 6.11. Jow. 3.1. Amo. 9.14.\x*; Jehovha ndokuwedzera zvese Jobho zvaaiva nazvo kakapetwa kaviri\x + Isa. 61.7. Isa. 40.2. Mako 10.30. Ruk. 18.30.\x*.
\v 11 Ipapo kwakauya kwaari vanin'ina vake vese, nehanzvadzi dzake dzese\x + 19.13.\x*, nevese vaimbova vazikanwi vake, ndokudya chingwa naye mumba make\x + 19.13.\x*, ndokuchema naye\x + 2.11.\x* ndokumunyaradza pachakaipa chose Jehovha chaaiva auisa pamusoro pake\x + 2.11.\x*; vakamupa umwe neumwe chidimbu chemari\x + Gen.. 33.19. Josh. 24.32.\x*, uye umwe neumwe chindori chegoridhe\x + Gen.. 24.22.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha wakaropafadza mugumo waJobho kupfuura kutanga kwake\x + 8.7. Jak. 5.11.\x*, nokuti waiva nemakwai zvuru gumi nezvina, nemakamera zvuru zvitanhatu, nechuru chezvipani zvenzombe nemakadzi embongoro churu\x + 42.10. 1.3.\x*.
\v 13 Wakazovawo nevanakomana vanomwe nevanasikana vatatu\x + 42.10. 1.2. 2 Sam. 12.23.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino wakatumidza zita rewekutanga \add kuti\add* Jemima, nezita rewechipiri Keziya, uye zita rewechitatu Kereni-Hapuki.
\v 15 Zvino panyika yose hapana kuwanikwa vakadzi vakanaka sevanasikana vaJobho; baba vavo ndokuvapa nhaka pakati pehanzvadzi dzavo\x + Num.. 27.1-8.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Shure kweizvi Jobho wakararama makore zana nemakumi mana, ndokuona vanakomana vake, nevanakomana vevanakomana vake, mazera mana\x + Gen.. 50.23. Isa. 53.10.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Jobho wakafa, akwegura, azara nemazuva\x + Gen.. 35.29. Gen.. 25.8.\x*.